      <title>德国央行称 2025 年德国经济几乎不会增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/german-economy-will-hardly-grow-in-2025-bundesbank-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国央行最新预测显示，德国经济在今年再次萎缩之后，到2025年将很难再增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/german-economy-will-hardly-grow-in-2025-bundesbank-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
